* Effective Partition\nKey Selection
** Low Cardinality
***_ Limited distinct values
***_ Date, region, category, status
***_ Not customer ID or transaction ID
** Align with Query Patterns
***_ Columns most filtered in queries
***_ Most common or critical queries
***_ Consider materialized views for other patterns
** Data Growth
***_ Scale with data volume
***_ Too coarse → huge partitions
***_ Too fine → many small files
** Even Distribution
***_ Avoid severely uneven partition sizes
***_ Bottlenecks from large partitions
@endmindmap
